  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1924380/extras/ac4b36f55478d306424319216666b3da.avif?t=1700668149\" width=620 height=350 /></span><br><br><strong>Dashing Orange</strong> is a fast-paced 2D platformer with a focus on precision and fluidity,<br>where you´re in control of a cute little Orange in a journey in this abstract world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1924380/extras/2da0b82fafad1ae85740e06e0f09f245.poster.avif?t=1700668149\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1924380/extras/2da0b82fafad1ae85740e06e0f09f245.webm?t=1700668149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1924380/extras/2da0b82fafad1ae85740e06e0f09f245.mp4?t=1700668149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Along the way, you’ll master jump, wall-jumping, wall-sliding, dashing and more than 25 new mechanics and traps as you leap from level to level, moving along, up and down the screen to put in your best possible performance in 75 challenging stages.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1924380/extras/6179558405282ace20bc03e02727d904.poster.avif?t=1700668149\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1924380/extras/6179558405282ace20bc03e02727d904.webm?t=1700668149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1924380/extras/6179558405282ace20bc03e02727d904.mp4?t=1700668149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>75 hand-crafted levels</strong> to test your skills<br></li><li> <strong>Tight controls</strong> - Jump over spikes, dash and climb walls, optimized controls for gamepads and keyboards<br></li><li> <strong>Paint</strong> levels with your orange juice by jumping, dashing or, well, dying<br></li><li> <strong>New mechanics</strong> being introduced every 3 levels<br></li><li> <strong>Start over immediately</strong> after a failed attempt</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1924380/extras/d0cfbf9419a57923abd47c8a7393a76e.poster.avif?t=1700668149\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1924380/extras/d0cfbf9419a57923abd47c8a7393a76e.webm?t=1700668149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1924380/extras/d0cfbf9419a57923abd47c8a7393a76e.mp4?t=1700668149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1924380/extras/ac4b36f55478d306424319216666b3da.avif?t=1700668149\" width=620 height=350 /></span><br><br><strong>Dashing Orange</strong> is a fast-paced 2D platformer with a focus on precision and fluidity,<br>where you´re in control of a cute little Orange in a journey in this abstract world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1924380/extras/2da0b82fafad1ae85740e06e0f09f245.poster.avif?t=1700668149\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1924380/extras/2da0b82fafad1ae85740e06e0f09f245.webm?t=1700668149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1924380/extras/2da0b82fafad1ae85740e06e0f09f245.mp4?t=1700668149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Along the way, you’ll master jump, wall-jumping, wall-sliding, dashing and more than 25 new mechanics and traps as you leap from level to level, moving along, up and down the screen to put in your best possible performance in 75 challenging stages.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1924380/extras/6179558405282ace20bc03e02727d904.poster.avif?t=1700668149\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1924380/extras/6179558405282ace20bc03e02727d904.webm?t=1700668149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1924380/extras/6179558405282ace20bc03e02727d904.mp4?t=1700668149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>75 hand-crafted levels</strong> to test your skills<br></li><li> <strong>Tight controls</strong> - Jump over spikes, dash and climb walls, optimized controls for gamepads and keyboards<br></li><li> <strong>Paint</strong> levels with your orange juice by jumping, dashing or, well, dying<br></li><li> <strong>New mechanics</strong> being introduced every 3 levels<br></li><li> <strong>Start over immediately</strong> after a failed attempt</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1924380/extras/d0cfbf9419a57923abd47c8a7393a76e.poster.avif?t=1700668149\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1924380/extras/d0cfbf9419a57923abd47c8a7393a76e.webm?t=1700668149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1924380/extras/d0cfbf9419a57923abd47c8a7393a76e.mp4?t=1700668149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
